snippet.title: Odd Man Out
snippet.description:
Odd man out is a channel dedicated to looking at middle ground between many of societies issues today. With everything becoming so polarized, it seems middle ground is somehow nonexistent. I discuss odd news, humor, world news, gaming, movies, politics, and general discussions as someone without a side to have.

"Joint undertakings stand a better chance when they benefit both sides."

~Euripides
